(143, '117.000 liá»u váº¯c xin Ä‘áº§u tiÃªn sáº½ Ä‘Æ°á»£c tiÃªm cho nhá»¯ng ai?', 173, '\r\n                <p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Bá»™ trÆ°á»Ÿng Bá»™ Y táº¿ Nguyá»…n Thanh Long cho biáº¿t 117.000 liá»u váº¯c xin Ä‘áº§u tiÃªn Ä‘Ã£ vá» Ä‘áº¿n Viá»‡t Nam sÃ¡ng 24/2. ÄÃ¢y lÃ  nguá»“n cá»§a Astra Zeneca.Â </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">CÃ¡c Ä‘á»‘i tÆ°á»£ng sáº½ Ä‘Æ°á»£c tiÃªm Ä‘áº§u tiÃªn gá»“m:Â </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">- NhÃ¢n viÃªn y táº¿ táº¡i cÃ¡c cÆ¡ sá»Ÿ Ä‘iá»u trá»‹ bá»‡nh nhÃ¢n <a href=\"/suc-khoe/dai-dich-covid-19.htm\" data-auto-link-id=\"5fed3436b00b7a0012bca1d1\">Covid-19</a></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">- Lá»±c lÆ°á»£ng biÃªn phÃ²ng Ä‘ang lÃ m nhiá»‡m vá»¥ táº¡i cÃ¡c chá»‘t</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">- Lá»±c lÆ°á»£ng cÃ´ng an táº¡i cÃ¡c khu vá»±c cÃ¡ch ly phong tá»a</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">- Lá»±c lÆ°á»£ng láº¥y máº«u, truy váº¿t</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">- Lá»±c lÆ°á»£ng phÃ²ng chá»‘ng dá»‹ch thuá»™c cÃ¡c tá»• Covid-19 cá»™ng Ä‘á»“ng</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">- CÃ¡c phÃ³ng viÃªn tÃ¡c nghiá»‡p táº¡i khu vá»±c cÃ³ dá»‹ch...Â </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Theo Bá»™ trÆ°á»Ÿng, Ä‘áº§u thÃ¡ng 3 sáº½ tiáº¿n hÃ nh tiÃªm sá»‘ váº¯c xin nÃ y. Cuá»‘i thÃ¡ng 3 cÃ³ thá»ƒ thÃªm 1,2 triá»‡u liá»u. Viá»‡c tiÃªm váº¯c xin Ä‘Æ°á»£c thá»±c hiá»‡n trÃªn nguyÃªn táº¯c Æ°u tiÃªn tiÃªm ngÆ°á»i cÃ³ nguy cÆ¡ cao Ä‘áº¿n ngÆ°á»i cÃ³ nguy cÆ¡ tháº¥p, vÃ¹ng cÃ³ dá»‹ch tiÃªm trÆ°á»›c, vÃ¹ng khÃ´ng cÃ³ dá»‹ch tiÃªm sau.</span></p>\n<figure class=\"image align-center\" contenteditable=\"false\"><img title=\"117.000 liá»u váº¯c xin Ä‘áº§u tiÃªn sáº½ Ä‘Æ°á»£c tiÃªm cho nhá»¯ng ai? - 1\" src=\"https://icdn.dantri.com.vn/thumb_w/640/2021/02/24/153506229101582248024287894745917651912804481-o-1614154677639.jpg\" alt=\"117.000 liá»u váº¯c xin Ä‘áº§u tiÃªn sáº½ Ä‘Æ°á»£c tiÃªm cho nhá»¯ng ai? - 1\" data-widt